/*!
* \page codetest Running Tests

The Intel HEX Class uses GoogleTest to perform testing. The test suite is
in the folder 'test.'

\section gtestbuild Building GoogleTest

The GoogleTest test suite uses CMake to build the testing environment.
Change to the 'test' director and do the following:

\code
cd test
cmake -S . -B build
cmake --build build --parallel
\endcode

\section gtestrun Running GoogleTest

To run the GoogleTest test suite, do the following:

\code
cd build
ctest
\endcode

If you're keen on generating XML JUnit output for Jenkins or a CI/CD 
environment, try:

\code
ctest --output-junit testRes.xml
\endcode

*******************************************************************************/
